================================================================
Informant
================================================================

The Informant spies on your forms and warns people if they try to leave a form that has been changed but not saved.

Learn more at: http://indielabs.com/entries/the-informant/

================================================================
Usage
================================================================

Simply include Prototype 1.6+ and The Informant.

<script src="prototype.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="informant.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

View informant.js for customization options.

